column_description: The field "international_tourists_number_Wan" records the number of international tourists
The field "international_tourism_earnings_Wan_dollar" records international tourism revenue
The field "domestic_tourists_number_Wan" records the number of domestic tourists
column_description_CN: 字段"domestic_tourists_number_Wan"记录国内旅游人数

column_description: The field "Domestic_Tourism_Earnings_Wan_Yuan" records domestic tourism revenue
The field star_hotel_number records the number of star-rated hotels
column_description_CN: 字段"star_hotel_number"记录星级酒店数目
